---
title: Lamb Steak & Creamy Pesto Sandwich with Potato Wedges & Caramelised Onion
description: Ditch the cutlery and get a little handsy with dinner tonight as you tuck into this decadent beef steak sammie. With sticky caramelised onion and a creamy pesto dressing, you’ll be transported to the pearly gates of gastronomy heaven.
